title: Sponsor Registration
description: Sponsors early check in from the lobby of PC West Ballroom.

title: Lunch
description: Get sandwiches from Which Wich after check-in!

title: Attendee Checkin
description: Hackers check in from the lobby of PC West Ballroom.

title: Opening Ceremony
description: Learn about the different tracks, get inspired by our speakers and let the hacking begin!

title: Hacking Starts
description: Good luck to everyone!!

title: Team Mixers
description: Get ready to mingle and find teammates!

title: Google Cloud Platform Workshop
description: Learn how to use Google's wide selection of cloud services suitable for any hack.

title: TritonXR VR Workshop
description: Learn comprehensive basics of virtual reality! VR equipment provided for those hacking a VR project.

title: IEEE Arduino Workshop
description: Beginner-friendly workshop for hardware, interaction with hardware components through software using bluetooth. All parts and equipment provided.

title: CSES NLP Workshop
description: Learn some Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques that you can apply to your hack!

title: ITradeNetwork Workshop
description: Learn and do some data analysis on a real dataset.

title: Northrop Grumman Workshop
description: Learn more about hardware programming and how systems from multiple disciplines interact with one another, aka systems engineering!

title: Dinner
description: Come get Mexican food from El Pollo Loco!

title: Boba Bar
description: Time for a tea break!

title: MLH Destress
description: Destress with other hackers, put together by MLH.

title: Facemasks
description: It's self-care time! Get your glow on.

title: Midnight Snack
description: Snack up and power through.

title: Breakfast
description: Start your day with some breakfast bagels and pastries!

title: Lunch
description: Get some pizza for the last hurrah!

title: Devpost Submission
description: Devpost due! You can still keep on hacking; just make sure your submissions are in.

title: Hacking Ends
description: Congratulations to everyone - you made it! Now relax, stretch and get ready to present your work.

title: Expo Judging
description: Show off your hard work to everyone in an expo. Judges will be walking by.

title: Closing Ceremony
description: Winners and prizes announced.
